  "body": "\r\n![unknown](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4932774/68664695-0732bc00-0541-11ea-8dd1-6f6e811a5f0a.png)\r\nas you can see on the image above, the badge is offset horizontally to the right, appearing detached from the icon it belongs to. I believe this was introduced here https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/9340\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nBadge is placed 16px to the right of the left icon edge and 6px up from the bottom edge or alternatively directly with its top edge.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"377\" alt=\"Screenshot 2019-11-12 at 11 49 09\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4932774/68665501-74931c80-0542-11ea-9bd3-b591287fee1a.png\">\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nBadge is placed somewhere else\r\n\r\n#### Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\nBadge is placed correctly and grows to the right with two digit numbers, so it's X position stays the same.\r\n\r\n[Figma](https://www.figma.com/file/aS1ct66VQ6V0cio7vSqS8UoG/Chat?node-id=16%3A357)\r\n",
